{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>棋盘上A点有一个过河卒，需要走到目标B点。卒行走的规则：可以向下、或者向右。同时在棋盘上的某一点有一个对方的马（如C点），该马所在的点和所有跳跃一步可达的点称为对方马的控制点，如图3-1中的C点和P1，……，P8，卒不能通过对方马的控制点。棋盘用坐标表示，A点(0,0)、B点(n, m) (n,m为不超过20的整数),同样马的位置坐标是需要给出的，C≠A且C≠B。现在要求你计算出卒从A点能够到达B点的路径的条数。<p><p>![](pic/1314.gif)<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"过河卒 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>从A点能够到达B点的路径的条数。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>给出n、m和C点的坐标。<p>","examples":"<input>8 6 0 4\n</input><output>1617\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1314","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}